.TH "ingenic_cgu_gate_set" 9 "ingenic_cgu_gate_set" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ingenic_cgu_gate_set \- set the value of clock gate register bit
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ingenic_cgu_gate_set
.BI "(struct ingenic_cgu *cgu "  ","
.BI "const struct ingenic_cgu_gate_info *info "  ","
.BI "bool val "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cgu" 12
reference to the CGU whose registers should be modified
.IP "info" 12
info struct describing the gate bit
.IP "val" 12
non-zero to gate a clock, otherwise zero
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Sets the given gate bit in order to gate or ungate a clock.

The caller must hold cgu->lock.
